  acc   INT-S                 ALV
  acc   LNTH-S                LN-Th
  acc   ET2-B                 ET2-sur
  acc   ETseq-B               ET2-seq
  acc   LNET-B                LN-ET
  acc   BB-B                  Bronchi
  acc   BBseq-B               Bronchi-q
  acc   bb-B                  Brchiole
  acc   bbseq-B               Brchiole-q
